HEADWORD: Megalomania
<hw>Meg`a*lo*ma"ni*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr.
<ets>megalo-</ets> + <ets>mania</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Pathol.)</fld>
<def>A form of mental alienation in which the patient has grandiose
delusions.</def>⟦br⟧
